server.osu_api_keys: Required. Need at least one: http://old.ppy.sh/p/api
server.all_players_have_supporter: All players get an in-game supporter (view friends and country rankings, osu!dircet)
server.display_clan_name: If enabled, in-game scoreboard will display the clan name
server.sensitive_words: Impact: Registered user name; in-game chat (Will be replaced by *)
server.seasonal_backgrounds: List of image urls. The osu! client will download and display these pictures

online_user_limit.[self]: The number of users allowed to be online at the same time. If it exceeds, login is not allowed

menu_icon.[self]: If enabled, osu! will display an icon in the main menu.

maintenance.[self]: If maintenance, players will not be able to submit scores, and create new mutiplay rooms.

mutiaccounts.[self]: Whether to allow a player to have multiple accounts. If not allowed, the player may be banned.

auto_ban.[self]: When pp is too high (unverified player), it will be automatically banned

in_game_registration.[self]: In-game registration settings (different from website registration)

login.retry_max: Allow login error retries in expires (seconds)

client_check.[self]: Check the player''s osu! client version when logging in

message.max_length: *Nullable. Message content exceeding this length will be trimmed

client_update.[self]: If enabled, the server will respond to osu!client''s check-updates request

session_recycle.[self]: Server will automatically logout timeout players at regular intervals. If you don''t understand, please don''t set it at will.
